overview: To celebrate 300 episodes of the CheapShow podcast, Paul and Eli put on their biggest live show to date - a two hour epic full of special guests including Paul Rose (Mr Biffo), Sanja Rose, Stuart Ashen, Ethan Lawrence, Octavious King, Sooz Kempner, Paul Putner, Brian Wecht and Pat Sharp! Filmed at The Harrow Arts Centre on Saturday 13th of August, 2022.
title: CheapShow 300: Live
